    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>Meanings which involve acquisition of information by formal or informal instruction overlap to a considerable extent with the domain of Communication (33). In some contexts the focus seems to be upon the fact of verbal communication, while in other contexts, it is learning which appears to be in focus. It is for that reason that a number of these related meanings are included in this domain of Learn, for example, μανθάνω[a] ({D:27.12}), μανθάνω[b] ({D:27.15}), μαθητής[b] ({D:27.16}), and ὁδηγέω[b] ({D:27.17}).</Content>
